 FontColor->RGBColor[1, 0, 0]]], "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.395423313266528*^9, 3.395423319561233*^9}, {
  3.3955067836453648`*^9, 3.395506783662636*^9}}],

Cell["", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.395506794501401*^9, 3.395506794513232*^9}}],

