  FontColor->GrayLevel[0.5]]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.3955145719768343`*^9, 3.395514660455441*^9}}],

Cell["Then", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.395514959989828*^9, 3.395514960316976*^9}}],

